{"type": "article", "id": 35286, "title": "用这两卷胶带，可以自己改造行事历｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-12-06T23:17:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 35542, "name": "icco nico"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 256, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161206183736925cgrL3MVC1WdyZ.jpeg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 18.0px 'Lucida Grande'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Nibyniebo by Justyna</h3><p>波兰艺术家 Justyna 在 Esty 上开设了一家名为 Nibyniebo 网店，出售她亲手制作的软陶壁钟。陶土特有的可塑性让 Justyna 得以将自己天马行空的创意转变成实物，每一个壁钟都像是在诉说一个童话故事。精致的配饰和鲜艳的色彩使它们看起来又像是一块可以下肚的蛋糕，让人忍不住想咬上一口。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/Nibyniebo\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些壁钟，售价从 80 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183956pmhfsK7L1gZ2vu48.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183956EesVjDU1Ox3SM4gA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183957lYgVvbtX5aUZF4uO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183957CZkjGmRNi7AwdQuU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183956brTlJcduxgBLO5zS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183956uV6KDZbxHMe1cOPw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>贴历 by icco nico</h3><p>对日历和行事历有点审美疲劳？日本文具商 <a href=\"http://icconico.ocnk.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">icco nico</a> 最近开发了一款名叫贴历的透明胶，从这个特别的名字你大概就能猜到它的作用。这款透明胶一组两卷，分别印有日期和星期，有了它就可以把任何一本笔记本打造成符合自己需要的行事历，自由控制日期的长度。贴历分为横向和纵向两种，一卷长 10 米，根据计算，可以规划超过四年的行程。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183815Q7AwMRvjYIDG3T5h.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333600\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183815douBYaCQiFOSt6fz.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.786400\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183815ZXPm94giIaD60ylJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LapPad Go+ by Innovation Syndicate Inc.</h3><p>加拿大公司 <a href=\"http://lappad.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Innovation Syndicate</a> 的设计师认为，未来的工作环境将逐渐脱传统办公桌的限制。为了让人们能够更好地进行移动办公，他们带来了这款名为 LapPad 的移动桌板：它重约 1.6 千克，内置了 8000 毫安的 USB 电池为智能设备提供续航保障。桌板上除了可以架起设备的凹槽之外，还自带一块鼠标垫（如果是左撇子的话，也提供订制服务）。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/124604521/lappadgo-the-first-mobile-workstation-w-built-in-c\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 129 加元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183840NlMGxwzALyP7jab6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694118\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183840M3C67jVK5yExrhYO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183840V75xqLr4OaMK2GCk.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183840Fy4Sni2XARkTL90j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.607353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612061838407EQ4gmSfpbcO8Hvl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Le réel et l'irréel by Zhuang Yicun</h3><p>从山水中获得灵感的设计我们此前也介绍过不少，你或许还记得那盏<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/32422.html\">光撒在山脉上的吊灯</a>。设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/zyc\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zhuang Yicun</a> 的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/40418513/Le-rel-et-lirrel\" rel=\"nofollow\">Le réel et l'irréel</a> 台灯则是一次将风景呈现在桌面上的尝试，以“存在和虚无”为主题，Zhuang 用高强度的 LED 和透镜制作光源，点亮后就会同打造成山脉形状的灯具通过虚实结合成为一个完整的画面。前后移动时，投射在墙上的光也会发生变化，模拟了日出和日落的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183937eZTAbfMtQw4xESj1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.585833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016120618393791Dniq7WLRVvdtmT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612061839373bN7IS1lTkx5vWju.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Temporary housing by Maja Jandrić</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.behance.net/MajnaSan\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maja Jandrić</a> 是克罗地亚萨格勒布大学（University of Zagreb）的研究生，这套以模块化为核心设计的<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43216427/Temporary-housing-in-the-context-of-crisis\" rel=\"nofollow\">临时住宅概念</a>是她的硕士毕业项目。Jandrić 在设计时尽量避免在搭建时使用到重机械或是额外的搭建工具，以鼓励难民们通过合作搭建出符合自己需要的布局，甚至形成一个新的社区。这些采用扁平化设计的轻质组件也减轻了难民和救援机构运输时的负担，提高效率。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183919K7SafeWRZY4thrux.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183919jgcDAvuLX9aB0lzq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183919BcDQLrxpEkFbPJle.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612061839205MhvxsaAX2ZtGk0o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183920lme9D5tbUkBOJoN0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612061839200lb2IiBruAvTWd13.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Haps Handy Bugs Pilers by GOOD!</h3><p>还记得那个把<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/32463.html\">昆虫和灯泡</a>结合在一起的包装创意吗？俄罗斯创意机构 <a href=\"http://good.kz/\" rel=\"nofollow\">GOOD!</a> 为墨尔本五金店 HAPS 设计的<a href=\"http://igormitin.com/Haps-Bugs\" rel=\"nofollow\">概念包装</a>同样是将昆虫的造型和各式钳子结合在了一起。这些虫子的外壳刚好覆盖住了钳子，配色也与其相对应，让平时看起来冷冰冰的五金件生动了不少。GOOD! 还为包装设计了配套标语：These BUGS fix any bugs。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183906YPCI7S8GbkEox5Jd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183906btD5AkRCHuEFn06W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183906m2kndXAu6bCQyWZG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.802500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161206183907kcVFipUdRIKZgzno.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}